eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2026%2F02%2F25095617%2Faltered-story-so-far-3-2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"0\"/></p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"timeline\" id=\"widget0_subwidget1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 px-4 2xl:px-0\"><ul class=\"grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-max grow\"><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\"></h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\">September</h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>Mandjet and the Western Armada rally at the City of Scholars at the request of Temera Singh.</li>\n<li>Preparations begin for a journey toward a luminous signal that appeared to the southwest, beyond an unbroken sea of clouds.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\"></h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\">October</h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>The Asgarthan fleet departs from the City of Scholars.</li>\n<li>The Expeditionary Corps explore a floating archipelago rich in Aerolith mineral.</li>\n<li>In Asgartha, Somayeh Bahman, the new Basilissa, is democratically elected.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\"></h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\">November</h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>Among all the Leviathans that have made their home within the archipelago, one of them—named Halua—systematically attacks every human convoy.</li>\n<li>A hunt is launched to put an end to Halua’s devastation.</li>\n<li>Thanks to the Musubi, a Bravos huntress bonds with the hostile Leviathan and manages to calm it.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li><li class=\"group grid-12 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col col-span-2 md:col-span-1\"><span class=\"border-primary-500 border-4 h-5 w-5 block rounded-full shrink-0 mx-auto\"></span><span class=\"w-px h-full block bg-primary-500 mx-auto my-1\"></span><span class=\"border-l-transparent border-r-transparent border-t-primary-500 border-t-[5px] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\"></h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\">December</h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>To reach the source of the light signal, the Asgarthans must cross the Whiplash, a circular storm whose raging winds prevent any ship from passing through.</li>\n<li>The Asgarthans manage to summon all the Leviathans they encountered along their route. By following in their wake, the exploration vessels succeed in crossing the Whiplash.</li>\n<li>First contact with the Reka civilization.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"\" data-attr-widget-name=\"content_block\" id=\"widget0_subwidget2\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 2xl:px-0 items-center text-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 w-full items-center text-center\"><hgroup class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-4\">394 AC</h1></hgroup></div><div class=\"md-medium md:lg-medium text-neutral-800 flex flex-col w-full items-center text-center\"><p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\"><img alt=\"altered-story-so-far-3-3\" data-nimg=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2026%2F02%2F25100008%2Faltered-story-so-far-3-3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Faltered-cms-prod-eu.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2026%2F02%2F25100008%2Faltered-story-so-far-3-3.jpg&amp;w=640&