] border-l-[5px] border-r-[5px] border-solid h-0 w-0 -mt-1 hidden group-last:block mx-auto\"></span></div><div class=\"pb-4 col-span-10 md:col-span-11\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-25%)\"><hgroup class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><h6 class=\"text-neutral-400 sm-bold-caps\"></h6><h5 class=\"text-neutral-900 title-6\">January-February</h5></hgroup><div class=\"lg-medium text-neutral-800\"><ul class=\"pl-4 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-circle [&amp;_ul_ul]:list-square my-4\">\n<li>After two months of rediscovery and negotiations, the two reunited peoples discuss the possibility of a lasting alliance.</li>\n<li>New Exalts are deployed to Asty, the Reka capital.</li>\n</ul></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>",
